Package: RSQLiteTmpDir
Type: Package
Title: Create and overwrite temporary directory for RSQLite
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Luigi A. Maglanoc
Maintainer: Luigi_maglanoc@hotmail.comThe package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: SQLite creates and uses temporary files. See [here](https://www.sqlite.org/tempfiles.html). This can cause unforseen consequences when handling large files, in particular on linux based systems. This package has a simple, single function which creates and overwrites a custom temporary directory for (R)Sqlite.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
